summary.description:
Today, a bit warmer for the feels like temperature (up 3.3°C) and outside temperature (up 2.6°C) and more moisture-laden outside humidity (up 8%) and rainfall (up 0.9 mm).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in light levels (up 6041 lux), pressure (up 10 mbar), and cloud levels (up 566 m).

The past week and month had observable variation in light levels (up 9683 lux) and cloud levels (up 971 m) when compared to today.
